long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Rakuten | Customer Service Helper is a Chrome extension to help Rakuten seller message with customers smoothly. It a free tool like Crisp magicRply or Drift GPT. Simply select the customer's question, then Rakuten | Customer Service Helper will feedback the reply advice that given by GPT-3.5 Chatbot.

ğŸš€ Feature
â— Provide canned responses or reply template by ChatGPT base on the question of customers.
â— Simply select the question content.
â— Edit feedback from OpenAI in Rakuten | Customer Service Helper to reply nicely to customers
â— Copy content by one click. 
â— Multiple output languages.

ğŸš€ Who is Rakuten | Customer Service Helper for
Rakuten | Customer Service Helperis made forRakutenseller, customer service staff or someone need reply customer's question to solve their problem.

ğŸš€ How to use it
â¡ï¸ Make sure you have a ChatGPT account
â¡ï¸ Simply select any online content by your mouse
â¡ï¸ Right Click your mouse to open menu and select "Rakuten | Customer Service Helper" to open the extension window
â¡ï¸ Choose what languages you need, and click "Ask for template"
â¡ï¸ The canned responses will displayed in the extension window in a minute.
